{"id": 61098, "date": "2025-10-10T04:00:12", "date_gmt": "2025-10-10T11:00:12", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=61098"}, "modified": "2026-06-11T13:08:55", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-11T20:08:55", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-october-10-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/10/10/kingdom-of-days-october-10-2/", "title": {"rendered": "October 10"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays at Grendel\u2019s Lair Coffee House in Philadelphia.</p>\n<p><strong>1976:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play a Lawsuit Tour show at Miami University in Oxford, Ohio. Based on the student newspaper clipping below, it seems that Bruce&#8217;s shows are not necessarily easy to book or facilitate due to Bruce&#8217;s legal battle with Mike Appel. At one point, the school seemed unsure about whether this concert would happen.</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-61098-12\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08-Growin-Up.mp3?_=12\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08-Growin-Up.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/08-Growin-Up.mp3</a></audio>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4744\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1976-1010/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1976-1010.jpg?fit=421%2C576&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"421,576\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quo