;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1335127294&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1980-10-10\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1980-10-10.jpg?fit=500%2C410&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-13374 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1980-10-10.jpg?resize=500%2C410&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"410\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1980-10-10.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1980-10-10.jpg?resize=300%2C246&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1983:\u00a0</strong>Bruce completes &#8220;Bobby Jean&#8221; during a mixing and overdub session at The Hit Factory in New York City.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/iGR_Rk74tOk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>Bruce appears on the cover of\u00a0<em>Rolling Stone</em>.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21725\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/rollingstone/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/rollingstone.jpg?fit=403%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"403,500\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"rollingstone\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/rollingstone.jpg?fit=403%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21725 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/rollingstone.jpg?resize=403%2C500&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"403\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/rollingstone.jpg?w=403&amp;ssl=1 403w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/rollingstone.jpg?resize=242%2C300&amp;ssl=1 242w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 403px) 100vw, 403px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2006:\u00a0</strong>Bruce&#8217;s Italian tour comes to a close in Rome, where he and the Sessions Band tour premiere &#8220;All the Way Home.&#8221; This show is available as part of Bruce&#8217;s official archive series.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/zfy9Q9vWsvU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/PiDrdW64Vs8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/2cqxXfofgH0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Bt7QcIUERsc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2007:\u00a0</strong>The Night Two rule is in effect in East Rutherford: Bruce and the E Street Band tour premiere &#8220;Adam Raised a Cain,&#8221; &#8220;Cynthia,&#8221; &#8220;You Can Look (But You Better Not Touch)&#8221; and the live debut of &#8220;Your Own Worst Enemy&#8221; at their Magic show at the Continental Airlines Arena.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZgVyP3aoOGw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0xAhY7nmSKk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HAgznnVjYwE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2016:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes a promotional appearance at The Harvard Coop to promote his new autobiography.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rpT2MYElKzM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21726\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2016-10-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-10-10.jpg?fit=1952%2C1407&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1952,1407\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1601323611&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2016-10-10\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-10-10.jpg?fit=758%2C546&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21726 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-10-10.jpg?resize=758%2C546&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"546\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-10-10.jpg?w=1952&amp;ssl=1 1952w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-10-10.jpg?resize=300%2C216&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-10-10.jpg?resize=1024%2C738&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-10-10.jpg?resize=768%2C554&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2016-10-10.jpg?resize=1536%2C1107&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2017:</strong>\u00a0Previews continue for\u00a0<em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City.</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-61098-13\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/101-Welcome.-I-Have-A-Magic-Trick-Bruce-Springsteen.mp3?_=13\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/101-Welcome.-I-Have-A-Magic-Trick-Bruce-Springsteen.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/101-Welcome.-I-Have-A-Magic-Trick-Bruce-Springsteen.mp3</a></audio>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>2019:\u00a0</strong>Bruce appears on <em>The Graham Norton Show</em> to promote his new film,\u00a0<em>Western Stars</em>.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Wbxd3A5E9Os?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p07qtsrh/player\" width=\"400\" height=\"500\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Tour premieres galore at shows across the years, plus Bruce makes a promotional book t